  "text": "In this subsection, we give a necessary condition for the global minimizers of (5) with the SCAD penalty (6) or the MCP [CITATION_1] . Specifically, we show that the global minimizers satisfy a set of KKT equations, which are nonsmooth but are Newton differentiable equations. Then we use Semi-smooth Newton algorithm to solve it. Now we derive the optimality conditions of the minimizers of (5) with p(z; λ, γ) to be p scad (z; λ, γ) or p mcp (z; λ, γ). This notation will be used in the rest of the paper for simplicity.",
